column2: Construct an ontology focused on the following: emancipation. Provide it in valid Turtle/RDF format, excluding any extra text.
column3: ```turtle@prefix rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> .@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .@prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .@prefix xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> .@prefix emancipation: <http://www.emancipation.org/ontology#> .emancipation:Emancipation rdf:type rdfs:Class .emancipation:hasYear rdf:type rdf:Property ;    rdf:domain emancipation:Emancipation ;    rdf:range xsd:boolean .emancipation:hasEffectedPopulation rdf:type rdf:Property ;    rdf:domain emancipation:Emancipation ;    rdf:range xsd:string .     emancipation:hasRegion rdf:type rdf:Property ;    rdf:domain emancipation:Emancipation ;    rdf:range xsd:string .    emancipation:wasTriggeredBy rdf:type rdf:Property ;    rdf:domain emancipation:Emancipation ;    rdf:range rdfs:Event .emancipation:ledTo rdf:type rdf:Property ;    rdf:domain emancipation:Emancipation ;    rdf:range rdfs:Event .rdfs:Event rdfs:subClassOf rdfs:Class .rdfs:Event rdf:type rdfs:Class ;    rdfs:label "Event"@en .    xsd:string rdf:type rdfs:Datatype .xsd:boolean rdf:type rdfs:Datatype .```
